{"tid":1716050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"各處仍有堵路交通受阻　運輸署呼籲放工市民策劃行程","createTime":"2019-11-13T08:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T10:01:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"342e56af3558cf8642dc262d94fca2abfeb34fba","tid":1716050,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:47:24.000Z","msg":"運輸署表示，由於各處持續有堵路，有多區的道路嚴重受阻，公共交通服務預料要一段時間才能恢復正常。其中東鐵綫全綫暫停服務，西鐵綫只提供由紅磡至兆康的列車服務，東涌綫只來往香港至欣澳，輕鐵有9條路綫要暫停。道路方面交通，吐露港公路來回方向要封閉，漆咸道南往觀塘方向近理工大學，干諾道中近康樂廣場等亦受阻。全港大部分巴士路線要暫停服務，只有約110條巴士路線提供有限度服務。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署總運輸主任何均衡呼籲，準備放工的市民要到交通營辦商的網頁，了解公共交通改動安排，並策劃行程，駕駛人士要留意各區有多組交通燈損毀，並小心忍讓。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491908-20191113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491908-20191113.htm&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QgmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=01357d55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491908-20191113.htm&h=7b22509d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491908-20191113.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7ee99b7640ecf08bcb217972aca73226a35a72e0","tid":1716050,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">繼續啊繼續啊繼續啊繼續到落實五大訴求煲底相見啊屌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民同我早早早早早起，繼續無限三罷，癱瘓交通，攬炒經濟！</span><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人已經退無可退！Neve forgive. Never forget. </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyOjWTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyOjWTe.jpg&h=fd7333c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cdzLMW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F